Codex Game Studios

This project adapts and reorganizes concepts, workflows, prompts, role
definitions, templates, and validation ideas from:

  Claude Code Game Studios
  https://github.com/Donchitos/Claude-Code-Game-Studios

The upstream project is licensed under the MIT License. This repository keeps
the MIT license and preserves attribution while changing the runtime packaging
from Claude Code-specific `.claude` assets to a Codex plugin plus project
template layout.
